		<h2> It's easy to join to a pool. </h2>
		<p> You can join a pool by any of theese methods </p>
		<ul>
			<li>Go to a friend's pool and click on the "Join" button</li>
			<li>Wait for a direct invitation to a pool. Click on the "Join" button</li>		
		</ul>	
